OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FA nurse has told ITV News that
OL,7,Fimpossible parking conditions at a
OL,8,Fbusy west Wales hospital left her in
OL,9,Ftears, facing hundreds of pounds in
OL,10,Fparking charges and eventually a
OL,11,FCounty Court Judgment.
OL,13,FCharlene Evans, who previously worked
OL,14,Fas an agency nurse at Glangwili
OL,15,FHospital in Carmarthen, says parking
OL,16,Fdifficulties regularly affected her
OL,17,Fbefore she had even started work.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
