PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FMs Evans told ITV News the parking
OL,7,Fconditions regularly caused her
OL,8,Femotional distress, with the demand
OL,9,Ffor a space frequently outstripping
OL,10,Fsupply.
OL,12,FShe said: "I was crying. I can't find
OL,13,Fa space. I was phoning the department
OL,14,Fthat I was scheduled to work in,
OL,15,Fsaying I can't find anything, ready to
OL,16,Fgo home and then thinking I can't go
OL,17,Fhome, this is my only income, I need
OL,18,Fto feed my children."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
