OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FOver an 18-month period, the agency
OL,7,Fnurse received seven parking charge
OL,8,Fnotices worth #50 each.
OL,10,FWhen asked how she felt when she found
OL,11,Fthe notices on her car after finishing
OL,12,Fshifts, Charlene said: "Deflated.
OL,13,FYou've given your all to look after
OL,14,Fsomebody, to keep people alive, to get
OL,15,Fthem home safely, support family
OL,16,Fmembers if they've lost loved ones and
OL,17,Fyou get out and you've got this car
OL,18,Fpark ticket on your window for doing
OL,19,Fall that and it's just like, really?"
OL,21,FIn the end the charges totalled #350.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FMs Evans told ITV News she believed
OL,7,Fthe charges had been issued unfairly
OL,8,Fand contacted the parking operator,
OL,9,FGroupNexus, to challenge them.
OL,11,FThe company did not accept her appeal
OL,12,Fand the dispute escalated.
OL,14,FThe debt eventually rose to around
OL,15,F#1,200 and a County Court Judgment
OL,16,F(CCJ) was issued against her, a ruling
OL,17,Fthat can have serious consequences for
OL,18,Fa person's credit record.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FAt that point, Ms Evans decided to
OL,7,Fchallenge the matter through the
OL,8,Fcourts but was faced with a difficult
OL,9,Fdecision. She explained: "The company
OL,10,Fstated that if I paid the original car
OL,11,Fparking charges they would remove the
OL,12,FCCJ, so I felt like I was between a
OL,13,Frock and a hard place, so I paid the
OL,14,Finitial charges."
OL,16,FHowever, she later decided to continue
OL,17,Fpursuing the matter and represented
OL,18,Fherself in court.
OL,20,FA judge subsequently ordered that the
OL,21,Fmoney she had paid be refunded.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FMs Evans believes the outcome was
OL,7,Fimportant not only for herself but for
OL,8,Fothers who may have found themselves
OL,9,Fin similar situations.
OL,11,F"I was absolutely adamant that this
OL,12,Fwas done unfairly and not just to
OL,13,Fmyself but to so many other people,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the parking company
OL,17,Fsaid: "GroupNexus accepts the court's
OL,18,Fdecision in this case. We will be
OL,19,Fpaying the ordered refund as directed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,F"However, we want to clarify the
OL,7,Factual nature of this case. Ms Evans
OL,8,Fdid not sue GroupNexus. She
OL,9,Fsuccessfully applied to set aside a
OL,10,Fprevious judgment that she hadn't
OL,11,Foriginally defended.
OL,13,F"The judge ordered a refund of the
OL,14,Ffees because they felt our initial
OL,15,Fclaim paperwork didn't contain enough
OL,16,Finformation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,F"Crucially, the judge explicitly
OL,7,Facknowledged that our parking terms
OL,8,Fand conditions had been broken, and as
OL,9,Fa result chose not to award Ms Evans
OL,10,Fany court costs or loss of earnings."
OL,12,FThe company added that it remains
OL,13,Fcommitted to keeping parking at
OL,14,FGlangwili Hospital "fair and
OL,15,Fmanageable".
OL,17,FHospital car parks are often managed
OL,18,Fby private parking companies because
OL,19,Fof the high demand for spaces and the
OL,20,Fneed to keep roads, drop-off zones and
OL,21,Femergency access routes clear.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
