PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FThe British Parking Association, which
OL,7,Frepresents the parking sector, has
OL,8,Fpreviously said enforcement plays an
OL,9,Fimportant role in ensuring spaces
OL,10,Fremain available for those who
OL,11,Fgenuinely need them, including
OL,12,Fpatients, visitors and healthcare
OL,13,Fworkers.
OL,15,FWithout parking controls, operators
OL,16,Fargue that hospital car parks can
OL,17,Fquickly become overwhelmed by
OL,18,Fcommuters or motorists with no
OL,19,Fconnection to the hospital, making it
OL,20,Fharder for patients and staff to
OL,21,Faccess services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FBut critics say enforcement systems
OL,7,Fcan leave frontline healthcare workers
OL,8,Fcaught between strict parking rules
OL,9,Fand the realities of overcrowded
OL,10,Fhospital sites where spaces are simply
OL,11,Funavailable.
OL,13,FLooking at the wider issue of parking
OL,14,FLisa Webb, Consumer Law Expert at
OL,15,FWhich?, warned costs can quickly
OL,16,Fescalate if individuals ignore parking
OL,17,Fcharges and subsequently cases
OL,18,Fprogress through debt collection or
OL,19,Fthe courts.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,F"If you genuinely think that you don't
OL,7,Fdeserve that charge, then you should
OL,8,Fbe appealing it," she said. "Anything
OL,9,Funfair needs to be challenged."
OL,11,FHowever, she added that motorists who
OL,12,Fknow they have breached clearly
OL,13,Fdisplayed parking rules are unlikely
OL,14,Fto succeed in challenging a charge.
OL,16,FAround 1,000 patients visit the
OL,17,FGlangwili site every day, alongside
OL,18,Fhundreds of staff and visitors.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FMs Evans accepts she parked in
OL,7,Flocations she knew were not designated
OL,8,Fspaces.
OL,10,FHowever, she maintains she often felt
OL,11,Fshe had little choice because of the
OL,12,Flack of available parking.
OL,14,FHywel Dda University Health Board has
OL,15,Fsaid it recognises the pressures on
OL,16,Fparking at the site and has taken
OL,17,Fsteps to increase capacity.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
