PN,43813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,FAndrew Carruthers, Chief Operating
OL,7,FOfficer at Hywel Dda University Health
OL,8,FBoard, said: "We cannot comment on
OL,9,Findividual members of staff who are
OL,10,Fcurrent employees or who have worked
OL,11,Ffor us in the past.
OL,13,F"Glangwili Hospital is a very busy
OL,14,Fhospital site and we do everything we
OL,15,Fcan to make parking as convenient as
OL,16,Fpossible for staff, patients, and
OL,17,Fvisitors.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1781871073
OL,3,CHospital parking under spotlight after
OL,4,Cnurse's dispute over charges
OL,6,F"We have an agreement with Gwili
OL,7,FRailway and offer 144 staff parking
OL,8,Fplaces at their site, just next to the
OL,9,Fhospital. This has freed up more space
OL,10,Ffor patients and they are in addition
OL,11,Fto the dedicated staff parking at
OL,12,FGlangwili.
OL,14,F"We encourage staff to park in the
OL,15,Fareas allocated. Inappropriate parking
OL,16,Fcan be dangerous for visitors to the
OL,17,Fsite and cause obstructions, impact
OL,18,Fflow of traffic including access for
OL,19,Femergency vehicles."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/14
